These samples use Angular 2.0 rc-6

Live DEMO here: http://www.syntaxsuccess.com/angular-2-samples
Documentation: http://www.syntaxsuccess.com/angular-2-articles

Here are the prerequisites for running the project:

1-npm run install-application (installs all dependencies, AOT compiles, tree shakes and bundles app into single file)

2-npm run start

npm run start

